PEOPLE
v.
BERG S235277 Supreme Court of California July 26, 2017 Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu and Cuéllar, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 4/1. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for In re Kirchner (2017) 2 Cal.5th 1040, 216 Cal.Rptr.3d 876, 393 P.3d 364, is dismissed. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)

Kruger, J., was absent and did not participate.
